quotes.text: "I'm honored to be called to lead the brilliant team at the CDC. We are ready to combat this virus with science and facts,"
quotes.speaker: Unknown

quotes.text: "uniquely qualified to restore morale and public trust"
quotes.speaker: Walensky

quotes.text: "She'll marshall our finest scientists in public health and experts at CDC to turn the tide on the crisis we're facing."
quotes.speaker: Biden

quotes.text: "So glad to hear this — looking forward to your leadership,"
quotes.speaker: Walensky

quotes.text: "What she brings to the table is both the infectious-disease expertise, but also the ability to restore faith in the CDC,"
quotes.speaker: Walensky
